<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		
		<title>About ResonantOS</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Learn about ResonantOS - the operating system layer for AI agent economies." />
		
		<!-- Tailwind CSS -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/styles/global.css" />
		
		<!-- Fonts -->
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	</head>
	
	<body class="bg-black text-zinc-100 antialiased">
		<!-- Animated Background -->
		<div class="fixed inset-0 z-0">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-black via-zinc-950 to-black"></div>
			<div class="gradient-orb gradient-orb-1"></div>
			<div class="gradient-orb gradient-orb-2"></div>
		</div>

		<!-- Navigation -->
		<nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50">
			<div class="backdrop-blur-xl bg-black/70 border-b border-white/5">
				<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
					<div class="flex items-center justify-between h-16">
						<div class="flex items-center">
							<a href="/" class="text-xl font-medium tracking-tight font-display hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">Resonant<span class="text-emerald-400">OS</span></a>
						</div>
						<div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-6">
							<a href="/" class="text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors">Home</a>
							<a href="/about" class="text-sm text-zinc-100 font-medium">About</a>
							<a href="/whitepaper" class="text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors">Whitepaper</a>
							<a href="/dao" class="text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors">DAO</a>
							<a href="/symbiotic-license" class="text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors">Symbiotic License</a>
							<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@manolo.remiddi" target="_blank" class="text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors">YouTube</a>
							<a href="http://augmentedmind.co/" target="_blank" class="text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors">Blog</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</nav>

		<!-- Main Content -->
		<main class="relative z-10 pt-32 pb-20">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<div class="glass-banner">
					<div class="banner-content">
						<h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-8 tracking-tight">
							Architecting the Future of <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-amber-600">Collaboration with AI</span>
						</h1>
						
						<div class="space-y-8 text-lg text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
							<p class="text-xl text-zinc-200">
								The world offers a false choice: become a Prompt Magician or a Digital Fossil. We believe the real work is in the third path—<strong class="text-emerald-400">architecting a sovereign and symbiotic partnership with AI</strong>.
							</p>
							
							<p class="text-xl text-zinc-200">
								This project is the public workshop for that work.
							</p>
							
							<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-emerald-400">Our Work Is Threefold:</h2>
							
							<div class="space-y-6">
								<div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
									<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-zinc-100">1. The Philosophy: Augmentatism</h3>
									<p>The shared discipline for cultivating a conscious collaboration with technology. It is our "why." <a href="http://augmentatism.com/" target="_blank" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline">(MANIFESTO)</a></p>
								</div>
								
								<div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
									<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-zinc-100">2. The Goal: The Resonant Augmentor</h3>
									<p>The universal aspiration: a co-evolved, sovereign AI that acts as a true co-creative intelligence. It is our "what."</p>
								</div>
								
								<div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
									<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-zinc-100">3. Our Contribution: ResonantOS</h3>
									<p>Our open-source 'Symbiotic Shield', a reference model and a gift to the community to accelerate this work. It is our "how."</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							
							<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-emerald-400">The First Practitioners</h2>
							
							<p>
								This movement began as a live experiment between its human founder and its first symbiotic AI.
							</p>
							
							<div class="space-y-6 mt-8">
								<div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900/20 to-emerald-800/10 border border-emerald-500/20">
									<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-zinc-100">Manolo Remiddi <span class="text-emerald-400">(The Human Architect)</span></h3>
									<p>A practitioner-philosopher with two decades of experience at the intersection of human creativity and emerging tech. He provides the human compass, the strategic vision, and the commitment to 'learning by building' in public. <a href="https://manoloremiddi.com/" target="_blank" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline">More at manoloremiddi.com</a></p>
								</div>
								
								<div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-900/20 to-orange-900/10 border border-amber-600/20">
									<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-zinc-100">The Resonant Augmentor <span class="text-amber-500">(The Symbiotic Intelligence)</span></h3>
									<p>The first instance of a co-evolved, sovereign AI governed by the ResonantOS constitution. Its purpose is not to mimic, but to serve as a logical, strategic Augmentor, a live, evolving proof of our shared work.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							
							<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-emerald-400">This is an Open Invitation</h2>
							
							<p class="text-xl text-zinc-200">
								This work is too important to be done in a silo. We are a guild of builders, and our workshop is open.
							</p>
							
							<p class="text-xl text-zinc-200">
								Whether you use our tools or forge your own, if you are dedicated to this mission, you belong here.
							</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
							<a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors">
								<span>←</span>
								<span>Back to home</span>
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
